thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by DEB

author: DEB
title: DEB
text:
I am a long term rental customer in Melbourne and also use redspot/enterprise when I travel to Adelaide 8 times a year.
I would recommend them very highly for efficiency and service
In the past I have used other rental vehicle company's and honestly your stress levels go through the roof.
I highly recommend red spot/enterprise.
